title: Cant log onto EUW
body: I am currently getting put into a queue of over 2000 while trying to log on but the server status says they are up?

replies.body: Our network team is currently looking into this!  We've got a [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page up, but we currently have a higher than usual queue.  Hang tight!
Same here, there is a problem with the EUW client login: http://status.leagueoflegends.com/?en_US#euw
